TMX Towable Mini Excavator is a perfect device that offers powerful, highly efficient, comfortable and convenient mini excavation needs. This unique towable excavator from Extend Manufacturing LLC is a perfect solution for do-it-yourself excavation. The TMX produces 6,600 pounds of digging force, making it one of the most powerful excavators in the world for its size and weight. With the 4-way blade and powerful hydrostatic drive action it is quick and easy to restore site with TMX’s Backfill Blade System. It features hitch system which allows you to work faster and is an energy saver. The zero rotation features in TMX Towable Mini Excavator allows you to get in and come out of tight spaces easily. You no longer need to get an air compressor or back-breaking jackhammers as you can easily power various hydraulic tools with this outstanding mini excavator. The TMX is all set to work with its in built trailer and lock-out drive hubs. You can tow it at highway speeds (55 mph) with most pickups, vans and other light duty tow vehicles. This versatile design can hold objects between the backhoe and the backfill blade. Latest upgrades to the ultimate TMX Towable Mini Excavator include multi functional joysticks, steel fuel and oil tanks, Plastic parts, oil and gasoline resistant, switchable travel speed control and electronic control circuits that reduce the amount of hydraulic hose by 30%. Apart from the efficiency, we have also ensured the comfort of the operator. The TMX features business class seating with an armrest, unobstructed view and clear seating position. To know more about this state-of-art machine you can call us on our toll free number 888.359.3002 or visit http://www.tmx-excavator.com/.
